      "to_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "content": "DONE — UI tweak complete. public/index.html, 1 file, +20/-10.\n\n**Part 1 — Slot suffix removed:**\n- Dropped `<span id=\"activity-filter-label\">` and `<span id=\"activities-filter-label\">` from the two tab buttons in HTML.\n- Removed the `activityLabel` and `activitiesFilterLabel` JS variables and both `.textContent = …` assignment lines. Tab headers now just read \"Events\" and \"Activities\" with no suffix for any slot.\n\n**Part 2 — Slot tag in global Activities view:**\n- In `renderTaskActivities`, compute `ownerSlot` from `agentStatuses` for each activity row.\n- `slotTag` renders as `<span class=\"activity-slot-tag\">:N</span>` only when `isOrchestrator === true`; empty string otherwise.\n- Tag is prepended inside `.task-activity-title`.\n\n**Slot tag style:** 10px, bold, muted text (`var(--muted)`), `var(--surface2)` background, hairline border (`rgba(255,255,255,0.06)`), 3px border-radius — same scale as the status/sha chips, no color accent. Title div updated to `display:flex; align-items:center; gap:5px` so the tag and text sit on the same baseline.\n\nNo build needed. Not committed.",
